112
00:08:38,730 --> 00:08:40,330
Don't let me starve to death.

113
00:08:40,549 --> 00:08:42,150
Don't let me freeze to death.

114
00:08:47,720 --> 00:08:48,780
Fire, don't go out.

115
00:08:48,970 --> 00:08:50,030
Fire, don't go out.

116
00:09:09,540 --> 00:09:10,310
The last one.

117
00:09:13,760 --> 00:09:14,890
I can freeze to death

118
00:09:17,160 --> 00:09:18,220
or starve to death.

119
00:09:21,430 --> 00:09:22,960
But I miss Yin Zheng so much.

120
00:09:28,180 --> 00:09:29,240
Can I

121
00:09:31,400 --> 00:09:32,550
see him again?

122
00:09:34,560 --> 00:09:35,310
Please.

123
00:09:37,770 --> 00:09:38,830
I miss him so much.

124
00:10:51,960 --> 00:10:52,590
I'm sorry.

125
00:10:53,270 --> 00:10:54,020
I'm late.

126
00:10:55,870 --> 00:10:56,470
Yin Zheng.

127
00:11:15,520 --> 00:11:16,560
Yin Zheng.

128
00:11:18,000 --> 00:11:18,870
Yin Zheng.

129
00:11:38,220 --> 00:11:39,460
I was scared to death.

130
00:11:39,920 --> 00:11:41,320
But when I thought of you,

131
00:11:41,430 --> 00:11:42,830
I wasn't scared anymore.

132
00:11:45,310 --> 00:11:46,770
Those bandits were stupid

133
00:11:47,400 --> 00:11:48,730
to let me get the chance.

134
00:11:52,000 --> 00:11:52,600
I'm sorry.

135
00:11:54,090 --> 00:11:55,350
What are you sorry for?

136
00:11:56,330 --> 00:11:57,590
As long as you are safe,

137
00:11:58,200 --> 00:11:59,800
you don't have to feel sorry.

138
00:12:01,080 --> 00:12:03,480
When Xiyuan told me that you were in danger,

139
00:12:04,080 --> 00:12:05,170
I was so worried.

140
00:12:07,950 --> 00:12:08,800
It's my fault.

141
00:12:09,740 --> 00:12:11,290
I've never been so scared.

142
00:12:11,960 --> 00:12:13,090
It's not your fault.

143
00:12:13,560 --> 00:12:14,490
On the contrary,

144
00:12:15,730 --> 00:12:17,130
I troubled you to save me.

145
00:12:18,290 --> 00:12:18,910
Sorry.

146
00:12:21,710 --> 00:12:23,380
Prince Zheng, Madam.

147
00:12:24,670 --> 00:12:26,330
Why are they calling me Madam?

148
00:12:26,400 --> 00:12:27,070
Put me down.

149
00:12:27,450 --> 00:12:27,730
No.

150
00:12:28,840 --> 00:12:29,840
Sorry, everyone.

151
00:12:30,320 --> 00:12:31,130
My wife is shy.

152
00:12:31,320 --> 00:12:32,320
Put me down.

153
00:12:32,610 --> 00:12:32,910
No.

154
00:12:33,680 --> 00:12:34,760
What are you waiting for?

155
00:12:34,760 --> 00:12:35,360
Follow up.

156
00:12:51,620 --> 00:12:53,070
Luckily, you're fine.

157
00:12:53,610 --> 00:12:55,600
