158
00:12:55,600 --> 00:12:56,080
Enough.

159
00:12:56,520 --> 00:12:57,980
We don't do this in our family.

160
00:12:57,980 --> 00:12:59,330
I'm back safely.

161
00:13:06,520 --> 00:13:07,380
Your Ladyship,

162
00:13:07,380 --> 00:13:10,490
Prince specially asked me to make this ginger soup

163
00:13:11,000 --> 00:13:12,130
to remove your cold.

164
00:13:12,260 --> 00:13:12,860
Thank you.

165
00:13:20,040 --> 00:13:21,300
Luckily, you're fine.

166
00:13:21,920 --> 00:13:23,920
Otherwise, I would not live either.

167
00:13:25,170 --> 00:13:26,900
I just comforted Ping and Zhan.

168
00:13:27,000 --> 00:13:28,730
You're acting like this again.

169
00:13:32,760 --> 00:13:33,960
Why are you coughing?

170
00:13:34,880 --> 00:13:36,130
Did you catch a cold?

171
00:13:36,640 --> 00:13:37,170
I'm fine.

172
00:13:38,230 --> 00:13:39,830
Have some ginger soup first.

173
00:13:40,480 --> 00:13:40,810
Here.

174
00:13:43,290 --> 00:13:44,420
Didn't I write to you

175
00:13:44,480 --> 00:13:45,980
that everything is fine here?

176
00:13:45,980 --> 00:13:46,910
Why are you here?

177
00:13:47,350 --> 00:13:48,950
I didn't receive the letter.

178
00:13:49,280 --> 00:13:50,080
Xiyuan told me

179
00:13:50,520 --> 00:13:51,450
you met bandits.

180
00:13:51,720 --> 00:13:52,840
I was really worried,

181
00:13:52,840 --> 00:13:53,700
so I came to you.

182
00:13:55,790 --> 00:13:57,520
You didn't receive the letter?

183
00:13:59,020 --> 00:14:02,060
Xiyuan used on me

184
00:14:03,080 --> 00:14:04,880
the trick she used on Shangguan.

185
00:14:09,160 --> 00:14:10,920
But I feel much relieved

186
00:14:10,920 --> 00:14:11,920
to be with you now.

187
00:14:15,510 --> 00:14:15,970
Zheng.

188
00:14:19,760 --> 00:14:20,860
Is Li Wei all right?

189
00:14:22,120 --> 00:14:23,780
Did the doctor come to see her?

190
00:14:24,800 --> 00:14:26,050
I brought ginseng

191
00:14:26,370 --> 00:14:28,060
for her.

192
00:14:37,880 --> 00:14:39,280
Can I have a word with you?

193
00:14:43,240 --> 00:14:44,370
Remember to take it.

194
00:14:53,160 --> 00:14:54,910
What do you want to tell me?

195
00:14:58,680 --> 00:15:00,680
Do you think you can hide everything

196
00:15:01,210 --> 00:15:04,470
after confiscating letters to the Garden of Tranquility?

197
00:15:05,570 --> 00:15:07,620
I don't understand what you said.

198
00:15:11,220 --> 00:15:13,960
Don't involve the inner courtyard with court affairs.

199
00:15:13,960 --> 00:15:17,120
If you put your dirty hands in the Garden of Tranquility again,

200
00:15:17,120 --> 00:15:18,780
you will die a terrible death.

201
00:15:33,520 --> 00:15:33,980
Prince,

202
00:15:34,380 --> 00:15:36,910
this was sent here urgently from Canghe Town.

203
00:15:40,130 --> 00:15:43,210
[We have completed the relief in Canghe Town, but Brother Jun doesn't want to handle the documents.]

204
00:15:40,130 --> 00:15:43,210
[Brother An, please help me check the disaster relief accounts of the Ministry of Revenue.]

205
00:15:40,130 --> 00:15:43,210
[Yours, Zheng]

206
00:15:48,300 --> 00:15:49,770
Zheng needs me now.

207
00:15:50,550 --> 00:15:51,550
I have to help him.

208
00:15:51,570 --> 00:15:52,090
Prince,

209
00:15:52,440 --> 00:15:54,100
didn't you plan to be neutral?

210
00:15:55,570 --> 00:15:57,960
I wanted to stay out of this.

211
00:15:58,710 --> 00:15:59,510
But after all,

212
00:16:00,590 --> 00:16:02,850
I have a better relationship with Zheng.

213
00:16:06,400 --> 00:16:08,860
Jun has written so many official documents.

214
00:16:09,040 --> 00:16:11,240
The articles are all claiming credits.

215
00:16:11,640 --> 00:16:12,680
Those people in Wuxiang Town

216
00:16:12,680 --> 00:16:14,210
are eager to praise him too.

217
00:16:15,110 --> 00:16:17,910
It's obvious that there will be endless troubles.

218
00:16:19,480 --> 00:16:20,420
Now it seems

219
00:16:21,370 --> 00:16:23,030
Zheng has kept his composure.

220
00:16:24,600 --> 00:16:25,800
My intuition tells me

221
00:16:27,170 --> 00:16:28,370
I should support him.

222
00:16:35,930 --> 00:16:37,510
It's not easy for Jun

223
00:16:37,960 --> 00:16:39,440
in Wuxiang Town.

224
00:16:39,870 --> 00:16:42,830
He still overcame so many difficulties.

225
00:16:45,560 --> 00:16:47,860
Everyone praised him.

226
00:16:49,040 --> 00:16:52,840
The magistrate of Wuxiang County also said he did a good job.

227
00:16:54,560 --> 00:16:56,820
Jun blowed his own trumpet.

228
00:16:57,320 --> 00:16:59,920
He's afraid that his merits will be forgotten.

229
00:17:00,560 --> 00:17:01,360
It's nothing.

230
00:17:01,620 --> 00:17:03,370
The disaster is over after all.

231
00:17:05,579 --> 00:17:06,760
As for Zheng,

232
00:17:07,040 --> 00:17:08,369
his official documents

233
00:17:08,400 --> 00:17:09,260
are two short.

234
00:17:09,640 --> 00:17:10,690
The accomplishments in his one wad

235
00:17:10,690 --> 00:17:12,750
are less than those in Jun's one page.

236
00:17:17,430 --> 00:17:20,560
I cleared the bandits' nest and collected all the gains.

237
00:17:20,589 --> 00:17:22,520
In Canghhe Town, there are 1,800,000 kilograms of leftover grains

238
00:17:22,520 --> 00:17:24,040
and 10,000 kilograms of charcoal.

239
00:17:24,040 --> 00:17:25,740
It's enough for the time being.

240
00:17:25,740 --> 00:17:29,070
The surplus will be sent to Xushan and Chongling for relief.

241
00:17:32,240 --> 00:17:33,970
He really cherishes his words.

242
00:17:35,790 --> 00:17:36,390
By the way,

243
00:17:37,250 --> 00:17:40,280
have you checked the accounts of the Ministry of Revenue?

244
00:17:40,280 --> 00:17:41,810
Please have a look, Father.

245
00:17:54,120 --> 00:17:58,010
Zheng only used this much for the disaster relief.

246
00:17:59,140 --> 00:18:01,810
He's quite frugal.

247
00:18:03,640 --> 00:18:05,590
Canghe is remote.

248
00:18:06,360 --> 00:18:09,620
Maybe he didn't spend much on maintaining relationships.

249
00:18:09,880 --> 00:18:11,320
As for Zheng,

250
00:18:11,490 --> 00:18:12,560
when you ask him to do something,

251
00:18:12,560 --> 00:18:13,330
he will do it well.

252
00:18:13,330 --> 00:18:14,860
But regarding civilities,

253
00:18:14,890 --> 00:18:16,150
he is not as good as Jun.

254
00:18:17,280 --> 00:18:19,480
Jun started from the Ministry of Rites.

255
00:18:19,800 --> 00:18:21,140
Wuxiang is a big town.

256
00:18:21,800 --> 00:18:23,380
It's inevitable for him

257
00:18:23,430 --> 00:18:25,350
to have some social activities.

258
00:18:26,430 --> 00:18:27,230
That's right.

259
00:18:27,430 --> 00:18:29,440
There are a lot of social expenses.

260
00:18:29,800 --> 00:18:31,260
But it's understandable.

261
00:18:32,040 --> 00:18:33,640
He came to a new place.

262
00:18:34,360 --> 00:18:38,350
He must show some courtesy

263
00:18:39,800 --> 00:18:41,530
in order to do things smoothly.

264
00:18:42,460 --> 00:18:45,410
Why won't Zheng do these?

265
00:18:50,640 --> 00:18:53,380
Wuxiang Town values the way of the world,

266
00:18:54,830 --> 00:18:57,890
so it might be difficult to get long-term development.

267
00:19:12,170 --> 00:19:14,300
All your memorials for reporting

268
00:19:14,370 --> 00:19:15,570
have been submitted.

269
00:19:16,160 --> 00:19:19,350
You will be rewarded when you wait upon the Lord at bedtime.

270
00:19:19,350 --> 00:19:19,870
Yes.

271
00:19:20,280 --> 00:19:22,380
Prince is the most favored now.

272
00:19:28,920 --> 00:19:29,290
Lady.

273
00:19:29,930 --> 00:19:32,220
Madam He summoned you for a talk.

274
00:19:35,110 --> 00:19:36,710
Why am I summoned by Madam He?

275
00:19:37,240 --> 00:19:38,100
Your Ladyship.

276
00:19:38,550 --> 00:19:39,070
Please.

277
00:19:54,940 --> 00:19:55,770
Would you

278
00:19:56,240 --> 00:19:58,120
copy all these scriptures

279
00:19:59,020 --> 00:19:59,820
to calm down?

280
00:20:01,920 --> 00:20:02,990
My Lady.

281
00:20:03,700 --> 00:20:04,570
I'm pregnant

282
00:20:04,850 --> 00:20:05,920
and my body is not agile.

283
00:20:05,920 --> 00:20:07,040
I'm afraid it's inconvenient.

284
00:20:07,040 --> 00:20:07,750
I know

285
00:20:08,480 --> 00:20:09,940
your health is important.

286
00:20:10,170 --> 00:20:11,700
I've asked them to stand by.

287
00:20:12,400 --> 00:20:12,930
Stand by?

288
00:20:20,610 --> 00:20:22,660
Are the four imperial physicians enough?

289
00:20:22,660 --> 00:20:25,020
They'll keep eyes on everything.

290
00:20:40,540 --> 00:20:43,140
