00:33:35,960 --> 00:33:37,420
The fever is finally gone.

580
00:33:46,110 --> 00:33:46,910
You know what?

581
00:33:48,290 --> 00:33:50,120
Everyone you've helped here

582
00:33:51,300 --> 00:33:52,430
sent you something.

583
00:33:54,550 --> 00:33:55,790
We fed you salt water

584
00:33:56,390 --> 00:33:57,590
and garlic porridge.

585
00:33:58,280 --> 00:34:01,080
In the end, I used the local method from my hometown

586
00:34:01,860 --> 00:34:05,240
and covered you with several layers of cotton blankets to make you sweat.

587
00:34:05,240 --> 00:34:07,240
That's why you got rid of the plague.

588
00:34:12,280 --> 00:34:14,260
You know I sleep soundly.

589
00:34:15,540 --> 00:34:17,739
I'm afraid I won't know when you wake up.

590
00:34:17,760 --> 00:34:18,960
It's better this way.

591
00:34:22,840 --> 00:34:23,449
Thank you.

592
00:34:29,360 --> 00:34:30,090
Not at all.

593
00:34:36,550 --> 00:34:37,750
This is the first time

594
00:34:38,900 --> 00:34:40,300
I've ever been so scared.

595
00:34:41,850 --> 00:34:43,690
I was even more scared than

596
00:34:44,230 --> 00:34:46,159
when I got lost in the forest alone.

597
00:34:49,949 --> 00:34:50,929
Get well soon.

598
00:35:01,780 --> 00:35:02,500
Yin Zheng.

599
00:35:03,920 --> 00:35:06,050
We promised to live together forever.

600
00:35:08,320 --> 00:35:09,570
We have to be

601
00:35:11,110 --> 00:35:11,910
healthy, safe

602
00:35:14,310 --> 00:35:15,720
and happy forever.

603
00:35:23,710 --> 00:35:24,090
OK.

604
00:35:54,320 --> 00:35:56,320
Prince is back from greeting the Lord and Madam this morning.

605
00:35:56,320 --> 00:35:56,720
Here.

606
00:35:57,630 --> 00:35:58,290
Have a seat.

607
00:36:07,830 --> 00:36:08,400
Prince.

608
00:36:08,900 --> 00:36:09,700
What's wrong?

609
00:36:11,770 --> 00:36:13,630
Today, His Majesty asked me again

610
00:36:14,020 --> 00:36:15,750
why Zheng hasn't come back yet.

611
00:36:16,650 --> 00:36:17,780
He said he's worried

612
00:36:18,250 --> 00:36:20,420
and wanted to send imperial physicians.

613
00:36:20,420 --> 00:36:22,400
We haven't heard from him for days.

614
00:36:23,670 --> 00:36:25,250
If the Lord wants to send imperial physicians,

615
00:36:25,250 --> 00:36:26,340
send them there.

616
00:36:27,320 --> 00:36:29,120
Canghhe Town is far away anyway.

617
00:36:29,210 --> 00:36:31,340
When the imperial physicians arrive,

618
00:36:31,370 --> 00:36:33,030
who knows if he's still alive?

619
00:36:33,240 --> 00:36:33,700
Xiyuan.

620
00:36:34,990 --> 00:36:35,990
Watch your mouth.

621
00:36:36,000 --> 00:36:37,330
Prince, calm down.

622
00:36:38,120 --> 00:36:40,850
You only told Magistrate Chu

623
00:36:41,530 --> 00:36:43,800
to be extra careful at the later stage of the disaster relief

624
00:36:43,800 --> 00:36:45,910
and keep all the doctors in the county

625
00:36:46,160 --> 00:36:47,690
in case something happens.

626
00:36:47,990 --> 00:36:49,410
As for

627
00:36:49,920 --> 00:36:51,320
what Magistrate Chu did,

628
00:36:51,490 --> 00:36:53,330
it's all based on his misunderstanding.

629
00:36:53,330 --> 00:36:54,860
It's none of your business.

630
00:36:57,250 --> 00:37:00,600
I never intended to harm him.

631
00:37:00,690 --> 00:37:01,670
Prince.

632
00:37:02,260 --> 00:37:03,200
I understand.

633
00:37:18,880 --> 00:37:19,530
Your Majesty,

634
00:37:19,530 --> 00:37:20,730
Her Ladyship is here to see you.

635
00:37:20,730 --> 00:37:21,330
Let her in.

636
00:37:21,480 --> 00:37:21,860
Yes.

637
00:37:32,290 --> 00:37:32,750
My Lord.

638
00:37:33,140 --> 00:37:34,550
What happened?

639
00:37:35,580 --> 00:37:36,620
Get up.

640
00:37:36,800 --> 00:37:39,240
Please forgive me for overstepping the bounds of propriety.

641
00:37:39,240 --> 00:37:40,400
May I ask

642
00:37:40,760 --> 00:37:42,480
if you are going to abandon Zheng?

643
00:37:42,480 --> 00:37:43,870
What nonsense is that?

644
00:37:45,330 --> 00:37:47,090
A rumor has been spreading for a while in the palace,

645
00:37:47,090 --> 00:37:48,850
saying that Your Majesty ignored Zheng.

646
00:37:48,850 --> 00:37:49,910
It's the same as exile.

647
00:37:49,910 --> 00:37:51,560
You're leaving him in Canghe

648
00:37:51,890 --> 00:37:53,560
to die.

649
00:37:57,270 --> 00:37:58,870
Is there really such a rumor?

650
00:38:01,680 --> 00:38:02,540
Your Highness,

651
00:38:02,600 --> 00:38:03,880
there indeed are rumors in the palace,

652
00:38:03,880 --> 00:38:05,320
but they're just nonsense.

653
00:38:05,320 --> 00:38:07,570
How could the Lord abandon Prince Zheng?

654
00:38:07,570 --> 00:38:09,860
This nonsense is ridiculous.

655
00:38:10,000 --> 00:38:11,690
I dare not tell you.

656
00:38:11,960 --> 00:38:12,820
Ridiculous!

657
00:38:13,310 --> 00:38:14,110
Investigate!

658
00:38:14,210 --> 00:38:15,670
You must trace the source.

659
00:38:15,970 --> 00:38:16,360
Yes.

660
00:38:16,800 --> 00:38:18,040
Since the rumor is false,

661
00:38:18,040 --> 00:38:20,500
please send imperial physicians to Canghe.

662
00:38:20,990 --> 00:38:22,520
I asked my mother's family.

663
00:38:22,580 --> 00:38:24,560
They said that Zheng is seriously ill.

664
00:38:24,560 --> 00:38:25,090
What?

665
00:38:26,470 --> 00:38:27,330
Please

666
00:38:27,520 --> 00:38:30,350
protect our son who I have wronged for many years.

667
00:38:32,240 --> 00:38:33,880
My Lord.

668
00:38:34,450 --> 00:38:35,370
My Lord.

669
00:38:35,900 --> 00:38:36,360
My Lord.

670
00:38:46,040 --> 00:38:47,350
Lady Wei, be careful.

671
00:38:47,730 --> 00:38:48,260
This way.

672
00:38:49,440 --> 00:38:50,360
The weather is so nice lately.

673
00:38:50,360 --> 00:38:50,960
Yes.

674
00:38:50,960 --> 00:38:52,890
Everything is getting better now.

675
00:38:58,880 --> 00:38:59,600
Yin Zheng.

676
00:39:38,960 --> 00:39:40,420
Why did you come out alone?

677
00:39:41,040 --> 00:39:42,700
Why are you wearing so little?

678
00:39:42,910 --> 00:39:44,960
You've recovered and forgot the pain?

679
00:39:44,960 --> 00:39:46,290
I have good news for you.

680
00:39:46,480 --> 00:39:48,000
His Majesty personally ordered

681
00:39:48,000 --> 00:39:49,040
to summon you back to the palace.

682
00:39:49,040 --> 00:39:50,970
He also sent imperial physicians.

683
00:39:52,270 --> 00:39:53,490
Prince, Lady Wei.

684
00:39:54,890 --> 00:39:57,030
Lady Wei took good care of you,

685
00:39:57,430 --> 00:40:00,480
so you recovered quickly.

686
00:40:01,280 --> 00:40:02,140
Physician Lin,

687
00:40:02,170 --> 00:40:03,800
you came here for nothing.

688
00:40:06,630 --> 00:40:07,710
You've recovered.

689
00:40:07,930 --> 00:40:09,570
