690
00:40:09,570 --> 00:40:10,640
Let's stay a few more days

691
00:40:10,640 --> 00:40:12,700
and make things harder for the court.

692
00:40:15,790 --> 00:40:17,190
You're indeed my Prince.

693
00:40:18,600 --> 00:40:19,830
Don't you like snow?

694
00:40:20,140 --> 00:40:22,400
This time, let's enjoy it to the fullest.

695
00:41:58,880 --> 00:42:00,700
Prince Zheng is here.

696
00:42:14,290 --> 00:42:15,420
Greetings, My Lord.

697
00:42:16,920 --> 00:42:18,000
Zheng is back.

698
00:42:19,240 --> 00:42:20,440
Are you all right?

699
00:42:21,560 --> 00:42:22,160
Yes.

700
00:42:22,880 --> 00:42:24,880
Thank you for your concern, Father.

701
00:42:28,840 --> 00:42:29,600
Yue.

702
00:42:31,030 --> 00:42:33,660
Your brother went to the northwest for disaster relief.

703
00:42:33,660 --> 00:42:35,590
He bore hardships, stood hard work

704
00:42:35,740 --> 00:42:37,000
and was seriously ill.

705
00:42:38,040 --> 00:42:39,570
He's back with glory today.

706
00:42:39,640 --> 00:42:40,840
