716
00:43:06,380 --> 00:43:07,780
In this disaster relief,

717
00:43:08,000 --> 00:43:11,520
Jun and Zheng did very well.

718
00:43:12,200 --> 00:43:14,360
Zheng has recovered.

719
00:43:14,460 --> 00:43:16,320
Come to court as soon as possible.

720
00:43:16,680 --> 00:43:16,980
Yes.

721
00:43:19,270 --> 00:43:22,200
