724
00:43:27,250 --> 00:43:29,850
Go home and recuperate.

725
00:43:30,640 --> 00:43:31,670
Have a good rest.

726
00:43:32,160 --> 00:43:32,670
Father.

727
00:43:32,800 --> 00:43:33,860
You're dismissed.

